    },
    {
      "id": "slide-09",
      "purpose": "explain",
      "layout": "process",
      "headline": "把生成、验证和修正连成闭环",
      "notes": { "speaker": "强调失败只重做局部环节，避免每次从头生成整套素材。", "durationSeconds": 55, "private": true },
      "visual": { "type": "workflow-diagram", "required": true, "status": "ready", "source": "html", "role": "explanation" }
    },
    {
      "id": "slide-10",
      "purpose": "key-claim",
      "layout": "quote",
      "headline": "AI 不替代判断，而是让判断更早进入流程。",
      "notes": { "speaker": "这句话是整场分享的原则页，读完后停顿两秒。", "durationSeconds": 35, "private": true },
